cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object recognition and tracking. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it introduces a new optimization approach for correlation filters. Additionally, it may be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories as it presents experimental results on diverse data sets.
